Upstream Curio schema files (schemas/frontmatter.v1.json,
schemas/events.v1.json) did not exist at scaffold time — they are
generated from curio-types in a later upstream phase.

A later integration pass must:
  1. copy both schema files here, byte-identical;
  2. write the PIN file per README.md (source repo, upstream commit,
     sync timestamp, sha256 of each vendored file);
  3. delete this marker.
